page.title: 11Fashion in J4
page.content:
We asked people of J4 what their choice of fashion is.The boys prefer Hi_Tec trainers where as the girls prefer Adidas. Five choices for jeans were made for the girls but the skin tight jeans are still the favourites. The boys like to wear Levis jeans as they are the favourite at the moment. The T_shirt most liked by the boys is Nike air tex top. The girls like ordinary plain tops to wear. Girls favourite type of socks are ankle socks which had{ 3 }votes.{5}votes came for the boys favourite socks which are white toweling socks {BOYS} { GIRLS}
